Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在時間線上遍地盛開的FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}What is reality?
