Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}沒錯  Naked Dive!  衝動的Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}只要好奇心不言放棄
